{"tid":1300243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「忘恩負義」點對得住傳媒大佬妹妹！","createTime":"2019-07-09T10:07:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T10:43:05.000Z","uid":261166,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"530a48722ce9b92d7d8d28ab013ed654718ecc75","tid":1300243,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:07:27.000Z","msg":"輿論同媒體係今次運動<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">功不可沒</span></span>，甚至係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唯一可以制衡警權的力量</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n近年，政府對媒體不同，包括：選擇性吹風，打壓網媒。<br />\n而反送中運動中，記者多次被警方不禮貌、甚至暴力對待、阻止採訪。身心承受長工時、高壓力，但無 10萬加班費 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n雖云兄弟爬山，各自努力，但滴水之恩 當湧泉相報！<br />\n所以，我提議，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">訴求加入「維護新聞自由」！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要求政府部門包括警隊，保持中立，尊重第四權，對傳媒一視同仁，保障編採自由！<br />\n<br />\n向各位傳媒大佬妹妹致敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660dcf675b8f192a99b8a9811773b93378dd5ae2","tid":1300243,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:08:06.000Z","msg":"請置頂、敬禮！"},{"pid":"a01993a70fd24a667d07ff7f162db3ddd34a7405","tid":1300243,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:08:19.000Z","msg":"歡迎入去討論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「長文慎入」勇武又好、和理非又好，自己香港自己救！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299934\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299934</a>"},{"pid":"62f56a0b1d708240b543ed27cc41a35e67335343","tid":1300243,"uid":1411,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:10:52.000Z","msg":"唔係唔支持<br />\n但係你加越多野就越易比人sidetrack左<br />\n最後佢淨係應承你保護新聞自由黎講話已經答應左部分<br />\n咁未令到成件事仲難落台同比人騎劫？"},{"pid":"26e74144a5786a18e3273ccc14e01613e5a4c559","tid":1300243,"uid":29128,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:11:24.000Z","msg":"應該係「停止妨礙新聞自由」<br />\n係一個指控黎"},{"pid":"93da904447adf0e77b6d9536b818d09529